Description: Desikan-Killiany-Tourville atlas for the 'ggseg' ecosystem.
    Provides a unified 'ggseg_atlas' object with both 2D polygon geometry
    and 3D vertex indices, for use with 'ggseg' and 'ggseg3d'.
